      <title>美国统计数据的侵蚀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-22/erosion-of-us-statistical-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国统计机构（包括发布月度就业报告的机构）面临财务压力，数据因此受到影响。从投资决策到地方发展资金，连锁反应影响到方方面面。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-22/erosion-of-us-statistical-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 14:01:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ChatGPT 推出两年后，交易员仍对人工智能“Roadkill”的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/ai-roadkill-fears-haunt-traders-two-years-after-chatgpt-debut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ChatGPT 的兴起引发了人们对人工智能将扰乱各类企业的担忧。聊天机器人发布两年后，其结果并没有像一些投资者预测的那样灾难性。但人们仍然很担心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/ai-roadkill-fears-haunt-traders-two-years-after-chatgpt-debut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对于新兴市场来说，“明年运气会更好”难以令人信服</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/for-emerging-markets-better-luck-next-year-is-hard-to-believe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[专注于新兴市场的投资者在过去一年里没有什么值得庆祝的事情。或者更确切地说，在过去十年里也是如此。现在，唐纳德·特朗普的关税和贸易战的前景让一些人考虑彻底放弃这些投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/for-emerging-markets-better-luck-next-year-is-hard-to-believe</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国对意大利金融业的举措引起罗马的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/french-moves-on-italy-s-finance-industry-stoke-concerns-in-rome</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利政府对法国在其金融业中影响力不断扩大的前景愈发担忧，目前两项即将达成的重大交易可能会重塑意大利金融市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/french-moves-on-italy-s-finance-industry-stoke-concerns-in-rome</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲大型股票正进一步陷入美国大型股的阴影中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/europe-s-big-stocks-are-shrinking-deeper-into-us-megacaps-shadow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺和诺德公司股价暴跌 930 亿美元，给欧洲最大的上市公司带来了最新打击，这些公司又花了一年时间徒劳地努力追赶华尔街最大股票的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/europe-s-big-stocks-are-shrinking-deeper-into-us-megacaps-shadow</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度正经历九十年代式的股市繁荣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/india-is-witnessing-a-roaring-nineties-style-stock-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[20 世纪 90 年代末美国股市的繁荣至今仍是历史上百分比最高的一次，帮助整整一代投资者致富。促成这一轮上涨的关键因素之一就是在印度扎根。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/india-is-witnessing-a-roaring-nineties-style-stock-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本债务不断增加 破产和自杀率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/bankruptcies-suicide-rise-as-japanese-struggle-with-mounting-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率上升和生活成本上升，越来越多的日本人陷入个人债务困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/bankruptcies-suicide-rise-as-japanese-struggle-with-mounting-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果 10 亿美元投资对印尼来说可能只是昙花一现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/apple-s-1-billion-investment-may-be-fleeting-win-for-indonesia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司提出将其在印尼的投资增加至 10 亿美元，以促使总统普拉博沃·苏比安托政府解除对 iPhone 16s 的销售禁令，印尼宣布获胜。但胜利可能只是昙花一现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/apple-s-1-billion-investment-may-be-fleeting-win-for-indonesia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求巴拿马降低过境费或恢复运河</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/trump-on-panama-canal-lower-fees-or-us-will-demand-its-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周六表示，巴拿马运河对美国海军和商船收取“过高的价格和通行费”，他要求降低费用，否则巴拿马应将运河归还给美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/trump-on-panama-canal-lower-fees-or-us-will-demand-its-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 00:37:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>危机进入第五个年头，中国房地产市场再度爆发危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/china-property-flare-ups-resurface-as-crisis-enters-fifth-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一家领先的开发商目前因违约风险而受到当局的关注。一家大型香港建筑商正在向贷款机构申请贷款延期。另一家业内同行正在出售北京一家标志性但基本空置的购物中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/china-property-flare-ups-resurface-as-crisis-enters-fifth-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
